			message: '#^Method SP\\Application\\Account\\Services\\AccountSearch\:\:getByFilter\(\) should return SP\\Domain\\Common\\Dtos\\QueryResult\<T of SP\\Domain\\Account\\Models\\AccountSearchView\> but returns SP\\Domain\\Common\\Dtos\\QueryResult\<SP\\Domain\\Account\\Models\\AccountSearchView\>\.$#'
